title: [Rosewyn's Magic Shoppe]
[Rosewyn's General Store]
[Rosewyn's Weaponry]
description: Enclosed by varnished ebonwood walls, the shop features a pile of striped throw pillows in the center of its mahogany floor.  A midnight blue rising phoenix tapestry hangs under the wooden ceiling.  Right near the front is a gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and a dovetailed oak table.
